display_long_description:
Monkeys gone insane takes players on an electrifying virtual adventure, drawing inspiration from the widely acclaimed and loved virtual reality title "Gorilla Tag." The game immerses players in a dynamic and lush forest setting, where they assume the role of agile and speedy monkeys. From the moment players step into this captivating world, they are greeted with a sense of wonder and excitement, knowing that they are about to embark on an exhilarating journey of motion, skill, and camaraderie.

As the game begins, players find themselves amidst the enchanting sights and sounds of the forest. The lush foliage, tall trees, and vibrant flora set the perfect stage for the monkey escapades that are about to unfold. With the virtual reality headset securely in place, players are instantly transported into the virtual forest, where their physical movements are mirrored by their nimble simian avatars. This immersive experience creates an undeniable sense of presence, making it feel as though players have truly become a part of this mesmerizing world
